t;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:BN\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:\r\n.0001pt;line-height:normal;background:white;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in;mso-bidi-language:BN\">Storage:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-bidi-language:BN\">256GB </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:BN\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:\r\n.0001pt;line-height:normal;background:white;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in;mso-bidi-language:BN\">Battery:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-bidi-language:BN\">4200mAh </span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:\r\nBN\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:\r\n.0001pt;line-height:normal;background:white;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in;mso-bidi-language:BN\">Rear camera:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-bidi-language:BN\">40MP + 20MP + 8MP </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-language:BN\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:\r\n.0001pt;line-height:normal;background:white;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in;mso-bidi-language:BN\">Front camera:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-bidi-language:BN\">24MP</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:BN\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:normal;background:white;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-bidi-language:BN\">The Huawei Mate 20 Pro is the best phone\r\nfrom the Chinese firm to date, offering up a heady mix of design, power and\r\nperformance with a few party pieces thrown in too.</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-language:BN\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:\r\n.0001pt;line-height:normal;background:white;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in;mso-bidi-language:BN\">Screen:</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;\r\nmso-bidi-language:BN\">&nbsp;The Mate 20 Pro packs a huge 6.39-inch display\r\ngiving you a huge amount of space for gaming and movies, and its QHD resolution\r\nand HDR10 support ensures everything looks great. There is a wide notch at the\r\ntop of the display though.</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:BN\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:\r\n.0001pt;line-height:normal;background:white;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in;mso-bidi-language:BN\">Battery life:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;mso-bidi-language:BN\">You\'ll get great battery life from the Mate\r\n20 Pro, and we regularly achieved a day and a half of usage from a single\r\ncharge during our review time with the handset.</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-language:\r\nBN\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:\r\n.0001pt;line-height:normal;background:white;vertical-align:baseline\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;\r\npadding:0in;mso-bidi-lang